pageContext.claim: “Wow! The Front Page @washingtonpost Headline reads, “A BOOST IN TESTS, BUT LACK OF TAKERS.” We have done a great job on Ventilators, Testing, and everything else. Were left little by Obama.”
pageContext.analysis: While the precise number of ventilators in the Strategic National Stockpile when the coronavirus pandemic has not be disclosed, there were likely thousands, based on numerous news reports on the stockpile over the years. There is no way Obama could have Trump a test for a virus that had not jumped to humans yet.
